column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, s.z as zphot, s.zErr, s.photoErrorClass, s.absMagU, s.absMagG, s.absMagR, s.absMagI, s.absMagZ, s.absMagG-s.absMagR as GR FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN Photoz AS s ON s.objID = p.objid JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS GN ON s.objID = GN.objID WHERE s.photoErrorClass = #
